{"tid":1195013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聞香港反送中遊行…韓國瑜：「我不知道，我不曉得」","createTime":"2019-06-09T13:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T04:59:38.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"512de7b339ce0abd79c7f7b8c7eca70b45ff1c40","tid":1195013,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T13:29:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%9E%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E7%AB%9F%E5%9B%9E%E9%80%99%E5%9B%9B%E5%AD%97-111536404.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%2581%259E%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2591%259C%25E7%25AB%259F%25E5%259B%259E%25E9%2580%2599%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25AD%2597-111536404.html&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq49VSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=ad40a9b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%9E%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E7%AB%9F%E5%9B%9E%E9%80%99%E5%9B%9B%E5%AD%97-111536404.html</a><br />\n<br />\n高雄市長韓國瑜9日率高雄市政府首長，參與高雄龍舟大賽，不過該組共四隊一同競賽，市府隊獲得第三名成績，韓國瑜笑稱「市府年紀偏高」，志在參與希望大家玩得開心。<br />\n<br />\n不過面對媒體詢問香港「反送中條款遊行」看法，韓國瑜竟連回稱「我不知道，我不曉得」，針對未來韓粉團體將以「一週一造勢」模式舉辦韓國瑜造勢大會，韓國瑜表示「都是被邀請參加，時間允許都會過去，但不會影響上班時間」。部分網友質疑說「花蓮造勢湧15萬人說法是膨風」，韓國瑜表示「我不知道，但人真的滿多的」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，面對國民黨立委陳宜民指稱，韓國瑜大選勝選後，連一聲感謝都沒有，讓他有些微詞，韓國瑜回應「這是感受問題，很主觀的，也許我謝的不夠，這我要檢討」，但韓國瑜也指出「其實我謝幾十次了，當面看到都有說謝謝，發LINE或電話都有表達謝意」。"},{"pid":"83ff8ca8743ae87ad3772acdb62ecca191a01e6d","tid":1195013,"uid":206895,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T13:33:11.000Z","msg":"條友淨係知道<strong>發大財</strong>"},{"pid":"af074ceb51d2d9bf5a49c5743800ec16ff4d8d57","tid":1195013,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T13:35:06.000Z","msg":"支持韓國瑜，支持韓總<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/HDi6jGy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHDi6jGy.jpg&h=26fdf5da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ankxCq3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FankxCq3.jpg&h=f2d5bc80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/sV2NEo9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FsV2NEo9.jpg&h=b1a26ead&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bcb1a75637c7fcee41cf8b06201264a8fd4849b4","tid":1195013,"uid":117679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T13:35:13.000Z","msg":"送中發大財?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ddfbcd19f2417533a40edc3190aa1e2c928793","tid":1195013,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}